               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210411-157-person1589">
                  EDWARD 
                  LEWIS
               <interp inst="t18210411-157-person1589" type="surname" value="LEWIS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210411-157-person1589" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210411-157-person1589" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a tailor, and live in Stanhope-street. I owed Stevens 1 l. 13 s. 6 d. On the 4th of April the prisoner brought some goods, with a bill and receipt for it. I paid him a 1 l. note and 10 s., and wrote back word why I did not pay the rest. Stevens called on me about eleven o'clock that night.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210411-157-person1590">
                  GEORGE 
                  SMITH
               <interp inst="t18210411-157-person1590" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
