                     <interp inst="t18210411-157-person1590" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I took the prisoner on Saturday. He begged forgiveness.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I met a friend, got drinking, and had the misfortune to lose it. I wrote to him to offer to pay it at 2 s. per week.</p>
               <p>LEWIS re-examined. When he was taken he did not say he had lost it. His wife said, in his hearing, that he had spent it - he made no reply.</p>
